Package: Friedman
Title: Tools for Daily Weather Time Series Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Abidur", "Rahman", , "abidurrahman@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for common tasks in daily weather time series 
    analysis, including growing degree days, frost risk assessment, and rolling precipitation summaries. 
    Designed for agricultural and ecological applications.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: dplyr, tidyr, ggplot2, lubridate
